{"blogid": "123577323", "writerAge": "码龄2年", "writerBlogNum": "6", "writerCollect": "23", "writerComment": "0", "writerFan": "1", "writerGrade": "1级", "writerIntegral": "75", "writerName": "AndrewZion", "writerProfileAdress": "..\\..\\static\\writer_image\\profile_123577323.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "111966", "writerRankWeekly": "437580", "writerThumb": "11", "writerVisitNum": "8326", "blog_read_count": "8075", "blog_time": "已于 2022-04-02 22:58:22 修改", "blog_title": "C++的字符串输入方式", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"../../static/bootstrap/css/csdnstyle.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"htmledit_views\" id=\"content_views\">\n<h3 style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\">1、cin输入字符串</h3>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><em>接收一个字符串，遇到空格和tab键结束接收，回车键表示输入结束；此外定义a[20]，则字符串长度要小于20，最后有个’\\0’(否则输入超过20的连续字符串会报错)。</em></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:left;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"68\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\1e35d960ed1b4978a9c770c9fb41dbb0.png\" width=\"139\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"49\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\c950bbf377724c16833bdad18f449709.png\" width=\"138\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"66\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\fa895b494eea406b987e7b64c0799c05.png\" width=\"132\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"50\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\0127d2bf5ce2453f8059c489017b82d8.png\" width=\"302\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:left;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<h3 style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\">2、cin.get()输入字符</h3>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><em>接收第一个字符并赋值给ch，不论第一个字符是空格、tab键抑或是回车键，以下四种不同情况输出分别是普通字符，空格符，tab键和回车符。</em></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"64\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\ded90098fd85432db15ca61c9290fc1e.png\" width=\"266\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"35\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\8dbc07b9867c4c1780bf9f61c8634783.png\" width=\"228\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"32\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\452764730dd94d95905f900a7b8e8b0f.png\" width=\"227\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"34\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\b66a2c4da3334b8a8fb65ea5687d6239.png\" width=\"278\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"47\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\63ddd408228b45a3bb998074558646fc.png\" width=\"216\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<h3 style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\">3、cin.get(字符数组名,接收字符数)输入字符串</h3>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><em>cin.get()</em><em>接收一行字符串包括空格和tab键(接收数量需减一，留一个位置给‘\\0’)，其中接收字符数一定要小于等于定义字符数组大小，不然一旦输入字符串长度大于数组大小会报错。</em></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"67\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\0a8a68a3ec334c0f8a809072d52dd7f0.png\" width=\"131\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"52\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\6ef3c9d080564141a8b8458d31778aad.png\" width=\"95\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><em>cin.get()</em><em>不传入参数是为了吃掉输入流中的回车。(比较下面两组输入输出)</em></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"113\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\f73a51877a884042900027671e2bd79c.png\" width=\"136\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"69\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\28d93f1d2e6e40c4bbdcb97ba104978e.png\" width=\"43\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"99\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\9db15e9c1d3c466abc748d68c4399159.png\" width=\"129\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"51\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\1df8d7285a2648dfb3ae5429aedbfb63.png\" width=\"39\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<h3 style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\">4、cin.getline()输入字符串</h3>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><em>cin.getline()</em><em>传入两个参数时与cin.get()类似</em></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"52\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\c0be1e37a1fc4825b2b146b1930bc60c.png\" width=\"141\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"35\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\815a665b19144dedae635000be377226.png\" width=\"82\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><em>与cin.get()区别在于当cin.getline()传入第三个参数时cin.getline(a,20,’f’)，接收字符串到’f’为止</em></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"48\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\2e2651cfb876421a91fa8f2e2dbf2b74.png\" width=\"169\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"35\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\bce64bf3dffc4f8ba2fe921c99a6a75d.png\" width=\"81\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<h3 style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\">5、getline()输入字符串(#include&lt;string&gt;)</h3>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><em>getline(cin,</em><em>字符串名字),getline()接收一个字符串，包括空格与tab键，唯一要注意的是，getline()属于string流，求字符串长度时不能用strlen()，应该用str.length()。</em></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"49\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\6f3886a542f44827af670813ba6293bb.png\" width=\"148\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"49\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\7f0d040075254d48817ac40c6a1f1343.png\" width=\"158\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<h3 style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\">6、gets_s()输入字符串</h3>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><em>gets_s(</em><em>字符串名字)输入字符串可以接收空格和tab键，回车结束</em></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"99\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\0ce5176ffdb342f29ecdb8856c151ed9.png\" width=\"131\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"67\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\a66dd2afc6044285849078c92c68b893.png\" width=\"169\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<h3 style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\">7、getchar()输入字符</h3>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><em>getchar()</em><em>接收字符串的第一个字符包括(空格、tab键、换行符)</em></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"51\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\1f4186635d914a58abe618419aec9c18.png\" width=\"107\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"35\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\8ea89c5b97ce4f9fac022b2a513fcb67.png\" width=\"69\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color:#fe2c24;\"><strong>注意所有字符串的输入(包括cin.get()、cin.getline()、getline、gets_s)，如果接在cin&gt;&gt;a输入流后，中间必须增加cin.ignore()用以吞掉换行符。</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><strong>本文参考这篇文章<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/xuptacm/article/details/88554704\" title=\"C++ 字符串的输入的几种方法_YULIU_的博客-CSDN博客_c++字符串输入函数\">C++ 字符串的输入的几种方法_YULIU_的博客-CSDN博客_c++字符串输入函数</a>然后经过我自己总结而成，如有不足请多指教！！！</strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n</div>\n</div>", "first_tag": "C++", "cpp": 1, "csharp": 0, "python": 0, "javascript": 0, "java": 0, "sql": 0, "php": 0, "time": "2022-04-02 22:58:22", "summary": "、输入字符串接收一个字符串，遇到空格和键结束接收，回车键表示输入结束；此外定义，则字符串长度要小于，最后有个否则输入超过的连续字符串会报错。、输入字符接收第一个字符并赋值给，不论第一个字符是空格、键抑"}